- Phase2: ...

## Reference Links
- [Flutter Theme Guide](https://flutter.dev/docs/cookbook/design/themes) - Official theming documentation
- [Issue #123](https://github.com/user/repo/issues/123) - Dark mode feature request

## Plan Steps (Progress indicator 30% - 3/10 done)
- [x] Create theme data models and enums
- [x] Implement theme provider with state management
- [x] Update UI components to use theme colors
- [ ] Add theme toggle in settings
- [ ] Implement theme persistence with SharedPreferences
- [ ] Test theme switching across all screens
- [ ] Update documentation with theme usage examples
```

## Integration with Development Workflow

- Create plans before starting major features
- Reference plans in pull request descriptions
- Update plans as requirements evolve
- Archive completed plans for future reference